			<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蚀灭的源焰之主s.assets/Image_18.png')" x="486" y="1069">
			</BitmapImage>
		</Group>
		<RichText x="1474" y="479" width="499" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特起身向前冲，使用铸影之暗和斫阳之曜各进行一次超大范围挥砍，分别造成<span color="#b8b8b8">25%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">20</span><span>),</span><span color="#ff9999">45%</span><span>伤害；随后巡弋至另一侧，再重复上述过程一次，巡弋期间场地将随机出现大量地喷，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">15%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">10</span><span>)伤害并留下渊泥。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="494" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特使用斫阳之曜与铸影之暗进行炎、渊、十字三段普攻，曜与暗的攻击分别造成<span color="#ff9999">25%</span><span>,</span><span color="#b8b8b8">25%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">10</span><span>)伤害并留下余烬/渊泥；每一段攻击都会产生相应的剑气，造成对应属性的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">15%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蚀灭的源焰之主s.assets/Image_19.png')" x="1456" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蚀灭的源焰之主s.assets/Image_20.png')" x="720" y="649">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蚀灭的源焰之主s.assets/Image_21.png')" x="64" y="192" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#654fa2" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#654fa2">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蚀灭的源焰之主s.assets/Image_22.png')" x="596" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蚀灭的源焰之主s.assets/Image_23.png')" x="576" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="499" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特释放寰宇界门，倾下数十秒的沦没黑雨，雨滴造成<span color="#b8b8b8">15%,3.75%,1.5%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">5</span><span>)伤害；黑雨间夹杂间断的磊块，磊块造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">35%,<br/>8.75%,3.5%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">15</span><span>)伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1200" width="470" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">图腾石碑：<span color="#bfbfff">24虚界</span><span>盾，破盾后破坏，并恢复全队100点元素能量寂特殊能量；一共有3个，全部击败后可令古斯托特主瘫痪15s并扣除古斯托特</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%</span><span>生命值。<br/>虚界护罩：成功破除后扣除古斯托特</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1474" y="735" width="497" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特将铸影之暗刺入空瞳，倏然一片虚空，鳞渊气泡如群星般散而又聚，而后湮毁，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">80%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">30</span><span>)伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>；期间古斯托特持有10s的</span><span textDecoration="underline">虚界护罩</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1247" width="499" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特借自垂悬天界的渊隧之门降下，绽放出惑光之叶，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">60</span><span>)伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="499" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特将漆黑之翼上的鳞羽大量洒下，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">15%,7.5%,3.75%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">2</span><span>)伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1474" y="223" width="502" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">继「星寰黑雨天刀磨」后，古斯托特凝聚日炎之力，使用斫阳之曜沿中心圆切线方向切开场地，造成大范围<span color="#ff9999">120%</span><span>伤害。该技能最多施放3次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蚀灭的源焰之主s.assets/Image_24.png')" x="1332" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/蚀灭的源焰之主s.assets/Image_25.png')" x="1312" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="499" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特将斫阳之曜与铸影之暗插入地面，造成<span color="#ff9999">25%</span><span>/</span><span color="#b8b8b8">25%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">10</span><span>)伤害并留下余烬/渊泥；随后两剑向前迸裂产生冲击波，造成上述相同效果；同时古斯托特蓄力朝玩家喷吐黑渊蚀光，持续造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">50%,12.5%,5%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">5</span><span>)伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
