		<RichText x="1474" y="991" width="504" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">古斯托特遁入深寂之霞，同时召唤3个<span fontWeight="normal" textDecoration="underline">图腾石碑</span><span>，并吸引玩家，持续造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>伤害，随后 每隔7s施放一次回响黑潮，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">30%</span><span>(</span><span color="#ccffbf">10</span><span>)伤害，持续30s；若未及时破坏所有石碑，则古斯托特施放「苍穹悬星万</span><span fontFamily="HP Simplified Hans">豗</span><span>雷」。以上伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">闪避帧均无法躲避</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
